statements.sql: select * from `business_settings` where (`type` = 'maintenance_mode') limit 1
select * from `categories` where `home_status` = 1
select * from `translations` where `translations`.`translationable_id` in (2, 3) and `translations`.`translationable_type` = 'App\Model\Category' and `locale` = 'en'

select `products`.*, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) and json_contains(`category_ids`, '{\"id\":\"2\"}') order by RAND() limit 12

select `products`.*, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) and json_contains(`category_ids`, '{\"id\":\"3\"}') order by RAND() limit 12
select `sellers`.*, (select count(*) from `orders` where `sellers`.`id` = `orders`.`seller_id`) as `orders_count` from `sellers` where (`status` = 'approved') order by `orders_count` desc limit 15

select `products`.*, (select count(*) from `order_details` where `products`.`id` = `order_details`.`product_id`) as `order_details_count`, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) and `featured` = 1 order by `order_details_count` desc limit 12

select `products`.*, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) order by `id` desc limit 8
select * from `reviews` where `reviews`.`product_id` in (1)
select * from `translations` where `translations`.`translationable_id` in (1) and `translations`.`translationable_type` = 'App\Model\Product' and `locale` = 'en'
select * from `categories` where `position` = 0 limit 12
select * from `translations` where `translations`.`translationable_id` in (2, 3) and `translations`.`translationable_type` = 'App\Model\Category' and `locale` = 'en'
select * from `brands` limit 15

select `product_id`, COUNT(product_id) as count from `order_details` where exists (select *, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where `order_details`.`product_id` = `products`.`id` and (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) and `status` = 1) group by `product_id` order by `count` desc limit 4

select `product_id`, AVG(rating) as count from `reviews` where exists (select *, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where `reviews`.`product_id` = `products`.`id` and (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1)))) group by `product_id` order by `count` desc limit 4
select `deal_of_the_days`.*, `products`.`unit_price` from `deal_of_the_days` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `deal_of_the_days`.`product_id` where `deal_of_the_days`.`status` = 1 limit 1
select * from `banners` where `banner_type` = 'Main Banner' and `published` = 1 order by `id` desc
select * from `banners` where `banner_type` = 'Footer Banner' and `published` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 3
select * from `flash_deals` where (`status` = 1) and (`deal_type` = 'flash_deal') and date(`start_date`) <= '2021-12-19' and date(`end_date`) >= '2021-12-19' limit 1
select * from `flash_deals` where (`status` = 1) and (`deal_type` = 'feature_deal') limit 1

select `products`.*, (select count(*) from `reviews` where `products`.`id` = `reviews`.`product_id`) as `reviews_count` from `products` where (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1))) order by RAND() limit 1
select * from `translations` where `translations`.`translationable_id` in (1) and `translations`.`translationable_type` = 'App\Model\Product' and `locale` = 'en'
select * from `reviews` where `reviews`.`product_id` in (1)

select `brands`.*, (select count(*) from `products` where `brands`.`id` = `products`.`brand_id` and (exists (select * from `sellers` where `products`.`user_id` = `sellers`.`id` and (`status` = 'approved')) and (`status` = 1) or ((`added_by` = 'admin' and `status` = 1)))) as `brand_products_count` from `brands` order by `created_at` desc
